{"tid":338772,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"中二病既毒撚係最痴線","createTime":"2017-07-28T12:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T07:12:42.000Z","uid":66951,"like":13,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"524f4148cb2d7bc81df854501b2d84f10a212427","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:44:41.000Z","msg":"話說今朝開左個post<br />\n預左無人討論<br />\n但估唔到惹左個中二病毒撚 騎劫左個post<br />\n同大家分享下佢有幾痴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n拍拖個時搵條女扑到佢個閪臭曬<br />\n跟住結婚個搵個清泉<br />\n這就是男人應該做的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#154<br />\n做人就係咁自私<br />\n鬼叫d女咁蠢，哄兩哄就可以同人上床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#160<br />\n做人就緊係要學識有d古古惑惑<br />\n咁樣自己嘅人生先過得比人好<br />\n正正經經做人係無好處<br />\n<br />\n#166<br />\n傻撚先會相信有報應呢樣野<br />\n根本呢個世界做過好多衰野嘅人生活一直都過得比人好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">睇睇下 發覺唔對路喎 好人好姐諗野咁癲？<br />\n跟住講左句 你好撚中二病<br />\n佢就開始上電啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n#178<br />\n已經看透呢個世界<br />\n做好人無好處<br />\nps你打d野都好撚中二病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#183<br />\n總之而家識女仔扑撚到厭就拋比第二個<br />\n結婚個時就同人講自己好純，搵個清泉結婚<br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻已經幾乎可能確認佢係中二病毒撚<br />\n但為左唔好搞錯 我都係起底睇下<br />\n一睇 原來係個暑假比老母迫去返parttime既毒撚（後尾先睇到個post，原來係自閉+躁狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n咁就開始泥漿摔角啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講講下 笠左水<br />\n因為無人幫拖<br />\n諗住會靜啦<br />\n點知有第二個人入黎嘈 佢又上返水（幾撚無用😂）<br />\n唔認笠水就例"},{"pid":"378613a4de0d797c8779f60f0bffe107f3e2b210","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"例牌啦 點知佢開始9up 搵野屈 又話我叫雞呀之類<br />\n<br />\n之後吹大左 無聲出 <br />\n第二次笠水<br />\n<br />\n之後當然有人圍爐個時佢又上水啦<br />\n呢個時候已經痴到頂點 又話同我老母拍av呀 話我唔去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果個post就係佢兩度笠水下爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f0d7a82687f5c6f4aed25ddb4e8517ba23a168","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:49:20.000Z","msg":"另外仲有個廢中 不過呢個小人物 不值一提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529bcb7bdb3d33e367f145ecaa4a94d4b485380e","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"最後<br />\n( Show Blocked User - .型男. )<br />\n多謝收睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00a3ff030a0f034699ab67924ce95a5e79cecd0","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b18ee8aeed58476b6bfd3dadfc82dc83b8fb29","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bad78f8983ae3ccb4ef7228b2a987260b496d3a","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"公道講句<br />\n<br />\n大家有眼睇<br />\n<br />\n邊個中二病發作扮情場騙子不遂係度發難😂 又笠水又老屈 仲比人發現係自閉仔"},{"pid":"fb28ecc1fd18ef52262c7cce4e56790461299967","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5