"},{"pid":"31d3b17dd218a0f40a7d86813213d48ea863c06e","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以上既說話可能7成連登仔都講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上連登 勿認真</span></span></blockquote><br />\n似乎佢係奉為真理咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個傻仔上壞腦姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n計我話一心一意就最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過扮情場騙子呢下好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乞衣扮富豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87ccedd9bf95e61f1264c5f4bccac345b7b46c5","tid":338772,"uid":55823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:14:32.000Z","msg":"圖都冇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279cfad586c0c8827d8bf4c391dcfa9619375fef","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖都冇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起底有link"},{"pid":"98a6640feb274d93c2a25dd1fc154b595097b2c0","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:50:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7accb8c2467ee22955d477e1d171f68a78524ee7","tid":338772,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T22:25:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19e32ac2c291fea68cc71b7946ca6d359e692605","tid":338772,"uid":130221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"哇，唔夠串，比我激到開多個post黎屌柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br